    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document introduces extensions to Mobile IPv6 that allow nodes to bind one or more flows to a care-of address.  These extensions allow multihomed nodes to instruct home agents and other Mobile IPv6 entities to direct inbound flows to specific addresses. [STANDARDS- TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
